{
  "stem": "26140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put-- chained us up and took us by lorries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 40 people-- 20 people in one lorry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- in the lorry wasn't-- not so bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They moved us to train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the lorries, they moved us to train and loaded us into train, from which we went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was to short journey, so I didn't feel anything except the change, that's all, which makes a difference, always, in a stable life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long did it-- the journey last?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About an hour, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were also taken together with us, with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We reached Auschwtiz, where-- where dressed and had our names given and-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to Auschwitz on the 30th of August, in the summertime, in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into Auschwitz, where I've been-- tattoo-- a tattoo written.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had the-- I seen the prisoners when they stood and looked at the-- the railway line, how we-- how we arrived and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked very miserable to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had striped clothing on, and it reminded me of prisoners which I've seen on-- on television.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they opened the train, couple of wagons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they started shouting, 'Alles out!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Alles out!' And they started beating us in order to make sure we moved quickly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when we were in the Auschwitz camp, they-- we had seen the Lagerkommandant, [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hoess, ?] who told us, don't forget you're not coming to a pension-- holiday camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You coming to do the concentration camp of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that, he-- he started asking, are there any priests or Jews?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
